function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Scos_Aria_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, Marker_Ruins_01, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idFollower, Marker_Ruins_01)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idFollower, AnimSet_InspectGround)
		
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idFollower)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Scos_Aria_Follower")
	
	-- Go to center of bridge
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, Marker_Waterfall, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idFollower, Marker_Waterfall)
		
		Hydra.QActorDelete(idFollower)
	end
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(NPC_Aria_Waterfall)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, Marker_TurDulra_RunTo, "npc_run", false)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idClone, 1.0)
	end
end

function Start()
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(Conv_Aria_Ruins01, idSelf, NPC_Aria_Loc01)
end
